[Quality of life and utility measures: clinical parameters for decision-making 
in health].

[Article in Spanish]

Campolina AG(1), Ciconelli RM.

Author information:
(1)Departamento de Medicina, Universidade Federal de São Paulo, São Paulo, SP, 
